step PAT (MINIAOD)

https://twiki.cern.ch/twiki/bin/viewauth/CMS/PdmVCampaignRunIIAutumn18MiniAOD
https://cms-pdmv.cern.ch/mcm/campaigns?prepid=RunIIAutumn18MiniAOD

MiniAOD campaign for Fall-2018 MC production
Starting RunIIAutumn18MiniAOD for DPG, POG 2018 samples.

Campaign: RunIIAutumn18MiniAOD

Release >= CMSSW_10_2_5
step: PAT
datatier: MINIAODSIM
eventcontent: MINIAODSIM
conditions: 102X_upgrade2018_realistic_v15
geometry: DB:Extended
era: Run2_2018
nThreads: 8
Request's memory: 5.9 GB

(step4)
cmsDriver.py step1 --mc \
--eventcontent MINIAODSIM \
--runUnscheduled \
--datatier MINIAODSIM \
--conditions 102X_upgrade2018_realistic_v15 \
--step PAT \
--nThreads 8 \
--geometry DB:Extended \
--era Run2_2018  \
--filein file:step-1.root \
--fileout file:step0.root


